task.summary: - fixed some bugs. removed material libraries and coverted everything to design library practices
- small bugFixes. - add primitive 'friend has left game' feature
- fixed applayouttoolbar bug for pre-loli - fixed new message notification bug - increased version to 1.4
-- added connect and login retry mechanism. will atempt to retry to login every xxx seconds, after 10 tries display error message
-- added connect and login retry mechanism. will atempt to retry to login every xxx seconds, after 10 tries display error message
- added custom notifications for PMs and ONLINE-OFFLINE status. Working with Global and Personal Checkboxes
- added custom notifications for PMs and ONLINE-OFFLINE status. Working with Global and Personal Checkboxes
- string concatenation optimization. This: " " + " ", replaced with stringBuilder
- done refactoring notification - refactored otto event posting
-added dagger 2 dependecy. maybe need refactoring, dont understand a shi.t about dagger2
- added possibility of close app without it being permanently running
- added some stuff. - added friends list sort by name and sort by status
- changed to support library 23.1.0. - refactores some broken shi.t from the upgrate - refactores dashboardfragment into MVP pattern
